data.description: Wow! Over a quarter of an acre BEACH-SIDE!  Live that Beach dream in the heart of Ormond Beach. This beach beauty is cradled between the Halifax River and the Atlantic Ocean. The backyard is fenced and private with restricted land behind so there are no rear neighbors! This low-interest loan is assumable for Veterans (only Veterans and buyer will need cash to make up the difference!) FYI, NO hurricane damage and NO flooding (NOT in a Flood Zone), just a gorgeous neighborhood! Amazing home just blocks to gorgeous Ormond Beach. Close proximity to wonderful restaurants, curiosity shops, grocers, and more in an area of well-groomed properties a half block to the Halifax River. This unique home has 3 bedrooms, 2 full baths, an office/work room, 2 different oversized living areas, a spacious di spacious dining room, and a modern kitchen with a large pantry, soft-close drawers, a lazy Susan cabinet, an appliance lift, and a reverse-osmosis water filtration system. The house has a flexible floor plan where the side portion of the home with 2 rooms, a bathroom, a private front entrance, and a "secret" wall-door that separates it from the main living areas can be a perfect setup for roommates, an in-law suite, or guests. The property has a nice screen room and a deck off the rear of the home. All of this with NEW kitchen appliances, NEW Range Hood,NEW Hot water heater, NEW light fixtures, a whole-house water filtration system, a whole-house surge protector, a new HVAC system in 2022, a roof 9 years new, an irrigation system, and hurricane impact windows and shutters for the front windows. Nothing that needs to be done, so bring your beach chair.This is a fabulous home in a great area.
